==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inasmuch
<hw>In`as*much"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[<ets>In</ets> +
<ets>as</ets> + <ets>much</ets>.]</ety> <def>In like degree; in like
manner; seeing that; considering that; since; -- followed by
<xex>as</xex>. See <cref>In as much as</cref>, under <er>In</er>,
<pos>prep.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Inasmuch</qex> as ye did it not to one of the least of these,
ye did it not to me.</q> <rj><qau>Matt. xxv. 45.</qau></rj></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Because; since; for; as. See
<er>Because</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inattention</ent>⟦br⟧
